Abstract: SMITH-Katherine Anne. Died on December 30, 1999 in Quakertown, Pennsylvania of pneumonia. She was 57. Her sisters, Margie Goldsmith and Lynne Miller, are saddened by her passing. Kathy is the daughter of the late Nancy Naumberg Goldsmith and Eugene Maurice Goldsmith.
